\n唔需要避諱講個死字，佢唔會因為你唔提死同自殺呢d字眼就唔諗死<br />\n所以你可以試下自然地同佢討論自殺既野<br />\n例如你可以問下佢打算點自殺，如果佢真係up得出一個詳盡既自殺plan,幾時用咩工具身後事等等咁即係佢好真心想死<br />\n如果佢冇一個自殺既plan其實佢自殺既諗法唔係真係咁深"},{"pid":"a5113761a881600f5174281e6f257e8fa54d70e0","tid":41130,"uid":59960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b8cf2b16caffa6846773041b2d6311c1d8b3ce","tid":41130,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"幫佢買重保險受益人寫你名<br />\n佢每次想死諗起益左你就唔會想死"},{"pid":"bad9732fddb3e50d0c20d8ce67f94663cbcc05cd","tid":41130,"uid":66111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7df9f27eafd5f4ffd3d2e50df2577eb25610d3","tid":41130,"uid":19464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>抑鬱症？<br />\n唔係咁易幫<br />\n陪佢係治標<br />\n陪唔到一世<br />\n試下搵左個本因先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢依家食緊藥<br />\n佢話因為覺得生唔生存都係一樣<br />\n所以想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到你個名覺得有d諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點都好 樓主記得發生咩事都唔係你的責任<br />\n心意已決的人阻唔到的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每次唔開心都會聽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝巴打你安慰我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}